articles.title: South African authorities blockade illegal mine with 4,000 people inside - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: South African authorities are blocking supplies for an estimated 4,000 people who are underground in an illegal mine.
articles.content:
NewsFeed
South African authorities are denying deliveries of food, water, and other basics to an estimated 4,000 people who are underground in an illegal gold mine.
